Package curam.omega3.user

Contains functionality that allows the capture of user specific state such as user preferences.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UserPreferences
    General container for all user preferences stored at session scope in the web application.
    UserPreferencesFactory
    A factory class that retrieves a user's preferences from the session object.
